node.text:
As we continue the celebration of the 20th anniversary of Hybrid Theory, we also wanted to celebrate the beginning of our fan club: Linkin Park Underground.
 
We released the very first Linkin Park Underground bundle to the LPU community on November 19, 2001. Fast forward to the present day, we are releasing LPU 20 which is heavily inspired by the design of archived items from LPU1.
 
Members with an LPU Full Access account can now shop the exclusive LPU 20 bundle + merchandise.

LPU Community Members and non-members can sign up at LPUnderground.com.
